OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMany areas dry, with some sunny
OL,6,Fspells. There will be scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, these most frequent in the
OL,8,Fnorthwest. Still rather cool in the
OL,9,Fnorth, but temperatures closer to
OL,10,Faverage in the south so feeling a
OL,11,Flittle warmer than Wednesday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of rain will move
OL,14,Fsoutheastwards across Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland. Drier elsewhere,
OL,16,Fwith clear spells and a scattering of
OL,17,Fshowers. Patchy fog and frost under
OL,18,Fthe clearest skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
