OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBands of rain moving
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards across Scotland,
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and northern England.
OL,8,FSunny spells elsewhere, but an
OL,9,Fincreasing risk of showers developing.
OL,10,FWarm in the south, chilly in the north.
